These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, milk, water
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, snake, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, bus, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person drinking juice is the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate  | water | milk    | juice       |
| Pet         | horse | goldfish    | snake      | bird |
| Transport   | quad-bike   | bus | helicopter | roller        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, plum, pineapple, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, nurse, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, scooter, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the mechanic##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the scientist##1
6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | pineapple   | plum | garlic     | cucumber      |
| Job         | firefighter | nurse | mechanic | scientist |
| Transport   | boat    | airplane   | scooter     | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, writing, hiking, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, disco, metal, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, french, american, argentine
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the french is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of metal##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the fan of disco##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the american##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | hiking | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | disco    | reggae | metal     |
| Nationality   | indian | american    | argentine | french    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, software-developer, paramedic, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, sailing, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, trike, tram, quad-bike
1. the paramedic is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the software-developer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the paramedic##1
7. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the fisherman is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | videographer | fisherman | paramedic | software-developer |
| Sport       | climbing     | tennis      | lacrosse     | sailing      |
| Transport   | trike | bike         | quad-bike      | tram        |

