.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, filmmaking, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, spy, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, handball, cricket
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | chess | gardening  | magic-tricks      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | superhero        | crime  | scientific       |
| Sport         | lacrosse | handball    | rugby | cricket |

