.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, analyst, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, thriller, sports, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, ambient, gospel, country
1. the coach is the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of country##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the fan of country is on the far left##1
5. the doctor is on the far left##1
6. the person watching sports movies is the analyst##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the project-manager is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | doctor | analyst | project-manager | coach |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | sports  | thriller | western   |
| Music-Genre   | country   | rock     | gospel | ambient       |

