.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, banana, radish, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, writing, sudoku, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, documentary, time-travel, fantasy
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
2. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is the person eating radish##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating peas##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | peas  | avocado | radish   | banana     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing   | gardening  | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel         | musical  | documentary | fantasy  |

