.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, documentary, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, japanese, spanish, malaysian
1. the person drinking coffee is the spanish##1
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the malaysian is the person drinking cola##1
7. the japanese is on the left of the malaysian##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | cola     | 7up | coffee |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | satire | documentary       | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | japanese   | malaysian | egyptian    | spanish |

