.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, peach, asparagus, potato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, pop, reggae, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, handball, cycling
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating peach##1
5. the person eating peach is on the right of the fan of classical##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | asparagus        | potato   | peach  | strawberry   |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | classical     | pop    | reggae       |
| Sport         | snowboarding | ice-hockey | handball | cycling |

