.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, garlic, eggplant
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, guinea-pig, lizard
1. the person drinking tea is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee    | milk | tea | lemonade        |
| Food       | eggplant | pepper  | broccoli | garlic     |
| Pet        | snake    | guinea-pig   | lizard  | fish |

