.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, fisherman, architect, engineer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, tennis, rowing, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, subway, taxi, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the engineer##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | electrician  | engineer | fisherman  | architect |
| Sport       | rowing | tennis        | handball | golf       |
| Transport   | motorbike   | subway          | train          | taxi       |

