.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, board-games, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, spy, comedy, drama
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, nigerian, brazilian, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the brazilian##1
7. the mexican is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | fishing   | board-games   | chess | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | epic | spy   | drama |
| Nationality   | mexican     | egyptian  | brazilian  | nigerian  |

