.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, collecting, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, d&b, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, climbing, cricket, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the fan of classical##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | gardening    | dancing        | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | d&b     | techno        | hip-hop   |
| Sport         | climbing   | cycling | cricket | surfing  |

