.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, spy, martial-arts, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, american, colombian, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, scooter, van
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the colombian##1
