3. the indian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
8. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | fantasy  | sports    | martial-arts    |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian  | indian  | american |
| Transport     | van  | boat | scooter | snowmobile        |

