.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, almond-milk, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, documentary, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person watching action movies is the person drinking juice##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person drinking milk is the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk        | juice    | lemonade | almond-milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic        | action   | fantasy  | documentary  |
| Sport         | volleyball | biathlon | rowing   | baseball |

