.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, cabbage, peas, pumpkin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, action, family, zombie
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, ferret, turtle
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating cabbage is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating peas##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person eating peas##1
7. the person eating peas is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | radish     | pumpkin   | peas | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie | family | action   |
| Pet           | turtle    | snake     | hedgehog      | ferret     |

