The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, journalist, chef, doctor
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, classical, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, thai, australian, indian
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the australian##1
2. the journalist is the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the thai##1
4. the fan of classical is the thai##1
5. the chef is on the far left##1
6. the doctor is on the right of the indian##1
7. the australian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | chef  | pilot | journalist  | doctor |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | ambient       | metal | jazz      |
| Nationality   | thai | dutch  | indian    | australian    |

