.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, malaysian, polish, canadian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, baseball, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, bike, bus
1. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian | polish | canadian |
| Sport         | handball | lacrosse | water-polo  | baseball  |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | helicopter | bus     | bike  |

