.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, electrician, freelancer, mechanic
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, american, chinese, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, handball, swimming
1. the electrician is on the left of the thai##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the freelancer##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
4. the chinese is on the far right##1
5. the thai is the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
7. the mechanic is on the far right##1
8. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | electrician  | freelancer  | writer | mechanic |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | thai | american   | chinese      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | handball    | cycling   | swimming         |

 